text: Pizzanya enak, service cepat. Akan kembali lagi!
Queue quite long at lunch, but staff stayed friendly.
Order arrived late and soup spilled inside the bag.
Ambience ok, steak a bit salty but cocktails were great.
Pelayanan lambat, barista terlihat tidak peduli. Meja kotor.
Loved the new salad. Portion cukup besar, worth it!
Sushi fresh, but soy sauce sachet missing in delivery.
Waited 35 minutes for pizza, anak sudah rewel.
Great service from Rina, super attentive. Thank you!
Kopi ok, sayang packaging cup kurang rapat jadi netes dikit.
